messages.content: Hi there! This is EZ Mobile Mechanic. What’s going on with your vehicle today?
Hello! Can you tell me what's going on with your vehicle?
sure sure I can well I've got a vehicle and it's not working it's
Got it! Can you please provide me with the year, make, and model of your vehicle?
um the gas smells like like diesel
Sounds like a fuel issue. Can you share the year, make, and model of your vehicle?
Thanks! Just to confirm, what's your name? And can you tell me if there are any other issues with the vehicle?
yeah sure my name is Billy John uh Gene
Great to meet you, Billy! So, we have a 1996 Hummer with a diesel smell. Would you like me to text you a quick estimate for the service?
